                      ‚Üí0 If(rc msg)‚Üź¬Į1('HTML root function "',(‚ćēCodeLocation),'.',t,'" is not a monadic, result-returning function.')
                  :EndIf
              :Else ‚ćĚ  otherwise it's 'file/folder'
                  _htmlEnabled‚Üź1
