    ‚ćĚ IncludeFns and ExcludeFns are vectors the defined endpoint (function) names to expose or hide respectively
    ‚ćĚ They can be function names, simple wildcarded patterns (e.g. 'Foo*'), or regex
    :Access Public
        ‚ąá r‚Üźget ipa
          r‚Üź‚ćé'_',ipa.Name
