    ‚ąá (rc msg)‚ÜźStop;ts;tokens
      :Access public
      :If _stop
          ‚Üí0‚ä£(rc msg)‚Üź¬Į1 'Server is already stopping'
      :EndIf
      :If ~_started
          ‚Üí0‚ä£(rc msg)‚Üź¬Į1 'Server is not running'
      :EndIf
      ts‚Üź‚éēAI[3]
      _stop‚Üź1
      Log'Stopping server...'
      {0:: ‚čĄ {}LDRC.Close 2‚äÉLDRC.Clt'' ''Port'http'}''
      :While ~_stopped
          :If WaitTimeout<‚éēAI[3]-ts
              ‚Üí0‚ä£(rc msg)‚Üź¬Į1 'Server seems stuck'
          :EndIf
      :EndWhile
      :If 0‚Č†TokenBase
          :If ~0‚ąä‚ćītokens‚ÜźTokenBase ‚éēTALLOC 2 ‚ćĚ any lingering tokens?
              {}‚éēTGET tokens ‚ćĚ remove them
          :EndIf
          TokenBase ‚éēTALLOC ¬Į1 ‚ćĚ remove token pool
      :Else
          {}‚éēTGET{‚ćĶ/‚ć®1=1 100000000‚ćł‚ćĶ}‚éēTPOOL ‚ćĚ remove tokens in the Conga connection number range
