                      msg‚Üź(0 2‚ćł‚ČĘinds)‚äÉ('Certificate with id "',ServerCertSKI,'" was not found in the Microsoft Certificate Store')('There is more than one certificate with Subject Key Identifier "',ServerCertSKI,'" in the Microsoft Certificate Store')
                      ‚Üí‚ąÜEXIT
